{"tid":2225102,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"識人好過識字 vs 識貴人好過識字 vs 識水魚好過識字","createTime":"2020-10-01T05:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T05:27:57.000Z","uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cea4ea819826edabdf41e15ab4eedacb1c07f209","tid":2225102,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:08:39.000Z","msg":"識人好過識字 vs 識貴人好過識字 vs 識水魚好過識字<br />\n邊個先岩?<br />\n<br />\n好多人都話識人好過識字:<br />\n愈識得多人，愈容易成功上位<br />\n但香港係一個小人當道既社會<br />\n未識到真正扶助你上位既人可能已經比小人呃左你唔少金錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n識到貴人，無論你識唔識字都好，貴人都可以無條件提攜你，當然識d字會較好<br />\n<br />\n識到水魚，可以sell到佢地買你公司產品，不斷開單，無數變爆數，但事前一定要識字呃到班水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6a123e197bfe82ad611ea0f2becbfe2e1eed99","tid":2225102,"uid":41085,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:10:54.000Z","msg":"識人好過識字<br />\n但唔代表你可以一隻字都唔識<br />\n識到一定既字會有助你識更好既人"},{"pid":"86f3142dcef96dd065f47eedcd7aff6c9de52c2a","tid":2225102,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:21:07.000Z","msg":"識水魚易上位<br />\n識人幫到自己<br />\n識貴人前途無限"},{"pid":"30f23f54b681d6720f7a93bc5b5a2c6f05eba23d","tid":2225102,"uid":242921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:24:07.000Z","msg":"樓主有見地！"},{"pid":"bb908426258722501b4c7d2c9ec4341a1812e33c","tid":2225102,"uid":90749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"af6a123e197bfe82ad611ea0f2becbfe2e1eed99","tid":2225102,"uid":41085,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:10:54.000Z","msg":"識人好過識字<br />\n但唔代表你可以一隻字都唔識<br />\n識到一定既字會有助你識更好既人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:27:57.000Z","msg":"啱<br />\n你字都唔識多隻<br />\n想去識人<br />\n人地都唔想識你啦"}],"pinned":{"pid":"86f3142dcef96dd065f47eedcd7aff6c9de52c2a","tid":2225102,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:21:07.000Z","msg":"識水魚易上位<br />\n識